{"id":206,"ayahs":[{"number":118,"arabic":"وَعَلَى ٱلثَّلَٰثَةِ ٱلَّذِينَ خُلِّفُوا۟ حَتَّىٰٓ إِذَا ضَاقَتْ عَلَيْهِمُ ٱلْأَرْضُ بِمَا رَحُبَتْ وَضَاقَتْ عَلَيْهِمْ أَنفُسُهُمْ وَظَنُّوٓا۟ أَن لَّا مَلْجَأَ مِنَ ٱللَّهِ إِلَّآ إِلَيْهِ ثُمَّ تَابَ عَلَيْهِمْ لِيَتُوبُوٓا۟ ۚ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ هُوَ ٱلتَّوَّابُ ٱلرَّحِيمُ","translation":"And [He turned in His mercy, too,] towards the three [groups of believers] who had fallen prey to corruption, until in the end-after the earth, despite all its vastness, had become [too] narrow for them and their souls had become [utterly] constricted they came to know with certainty that there is no refuge from God other than [a return] unto Him; and thereupon He turned again unto them in His mercy, so that they might repent: for, verily, God alone is an acceptor of repentance, a dispenser of grace.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1353.mp3","surahId":9,"words":[{"id":75955,"position":1,"arabic":"وَعَلَى","translation":"এবং উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_118_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75956,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلثَّلَـٰثَةِ","translation":"(ঐ) তিনজনের (ক্ষমা করলেন)","audioUrl":"wbw/009_118_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75957,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_118_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75958,"position":4,"arabic":"خُلِّفُوا۟","translation":"(তাদের সিদ্ধান্ত)স্হগিত রাখা হয়েছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/009_118_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75959,"position":5,"arabic":"حَتَّىٰٓ","translation":"এমনকি","audioUrl":"wbw/009_118_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75960,"position":6,"arabic":"إِذَا","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/009_118_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75961,"position":7,"arabic":"ضَاقَتْ","translation":"সংকুচিত হয়ে গেলো","audioUrl":"wbw/009_118_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75962,"position":8,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمُ","translation":"জন্যে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_118_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7